Random Art Piece of the Day

Random Art Piece of the Day is a full-stack web application that displays a random piece of art from the Art Institute of Chicago's API. 
Each time the page is loaded, a new random artwork is fetched and shown on the website.

Technologies:
    Node.js
    Express.js
    EJS
    HTML, CSS, and JavaScript

After clonning the repisotory to your local machine, find the cloned folder under code editor and you'll need to enter following prompt to install NPM packages;

npm init
npm install
npm install axios ejs express node nodemon path

When installments are done, in order to run the project you'll need to enter following prompt;
nodemon app.js

Then open your web browser and go to http://localhost:5555 to access the web project.

